  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The graph of the function <span class=\"italic\">f</span> is a line in the <span class=\"italic \">xy</span>-plane. If the line has slope <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"three-fourths \"></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 0, equals 3\"></span></span>, which of the following defines <span class=\"italic\">f</span>?</p>\n",
