  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. The equation for the function <span class=\"italic\">f</span> in the <span class=\"italic\">xy</span>-plane can be represented by <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, m x plus b\"></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">m</span> is the slope and <span class=\"italic\">b</span> is the <span class=\"italic\">y</span>-coordinate of the <span class=\"italic\">y</span>-intercept. Since it&rsquo;s given that the line has a slope of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"three fourths\"></span>, it follows that <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"m equals three fourths \"></span> in <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, m x plus b\"></span>, which yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"y equals, three fourths x, plus b\"></span>. It&rsquo;s given that <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 0 equals 3\"></span>. This implies that the graph of the function <span class=\"italic\">f</span> in the <span class=\"italic\">xy</span>-plane passes through the point <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"with coordinates 0 comma 3\"></span>. Thus, the <span class=\"italic\">y</span>-coordinate of the <span class=\"italic\">y</span>-intercept of the graph is 3, so <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"b equals 3\"></span> in <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, three fourths x, plus b\"></span>, which yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, three fourths x, plus 3\"></span>. Therefore, the equation <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, three fourths x, plus 3\"></span> defines the function <span class=\"italic\">f. </span><p>Choice A is incorrect and may result from a sign error for the <span class=\"italic\">y</span>-intercept. Choice C is incorrect and may result from using the denominator of the given slope as <span class=\"italic\">m</span> in <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, m x plus b\"></span>, in addition to a sign error for the <span class=\"italic\">y</span>-intercept. Choice D is incorrect and may result from using the denominator of the given slope as <span class=\"italic\">m</span> in <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x equals, m x plus b\"></span>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p></p>\n",
